reviewText: great dvd for a fan to enjoy acoustic versions of some of Unwritten laws best songs.

Pretty fun to watch.
Living near Yellowstone Park it is neat seeing them playing in that environment.  I think the funniest part was watching them play the redneck bar with the drunk redneck chick dancing on the table.
I think its a good album / dvd and a good look, they seem baked a good chunk of the time but sounds good all the same.
I had never heard of Unwritten Law but was turned onto them by my son, I just love this CD and DVD, check it out it won't disappoint
